'''第70届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[1997年电影|1997年最优秀电影]]的一场晚会，于[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]1998年3月23日下午18点（[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]晚上21点）在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的神殿礼堂举行，共计颁发了24座[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（也称[[学院奖|学院奖]]）。晚会通过[[美国广播公司|ABC]]在[[美国电视|美国]]直播，由吉尔·凯茨担任[[制片人|制片人]]，路易斯·{{lang|en|J}}·霍维茨导演<ref>{{cite news | last = Snow | first = Shauna | title = Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and international news services and the nation's press. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222171218/http://articles.latimes.com/1997/dec/12/entertainment/ca-63145/2 | deadurl = no | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1997/dec/12/entertainment/ca-63145/2 | accessdate = 2014-03-29 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 1997-12-12 | archivedate = 2014-02-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Horvitz to helm Academy broadcast | url = http://variety.com/1998/more/news/jan-8-1998-1117434573/ | accessdate = 2014-03-29 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 1998-01-08 | archivedate = 2013-11-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131107092342/http://variety.com/1998/more/news/jan-8-1998-1117434573/}}</ref>。[[男演员|男演员]][[比利·克里斯托|比利·克里斯托]]第六度担任主持人<ref>{{cite news | title = Crystal set for sixth Oscar stint | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223205737/http://variety.com/1997/more/news/dec-21-1997-111799971/ | url = http://variety.com/1997/more/news/dec-21-1997-111799971/ | accessdate = 2014-03-29 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 1997-12-21 | archivedate = 2014-02-23}}</ref>。他曾于1990年的[[第62届奥斯卡金像奖|第62届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]中首度主持，而上一次担任主持人则是在一年前举行的[[第69届奥斯卡金像奖|第69届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Crowe | first = Jerry | title = Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and international news services and the nation's press. | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1997/dec/20/entertainment/ca-382 | accessdate = 2014-03-29 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 1997-12-20 | archivedate = 2013-11-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131106065228/http://articles.latimes.com/1997/dec/20/entertainment/ca-382}}</ref>。近一个月前的2月28日，女演员[[艾希莉·賈德|艾希莉·賈德]]在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亞州)|比佛利山]]的[[比佛利山威尔希尔酒店|威尔希尔丽晶酒店]]主持颁发了[[奥斯卡科技成果奖|奥斯卡科技成果奖]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Judd named presenter at 70th Oscars | url = http://variety.com/1998/more/news/from-feb-20-1117467952/ | accessdate = 2014-03-29 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 1998-02-20 | archivedate = 2014-02-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140226132326/http://variety.com/1998/more/news/from-feb-20-1117467952/}}</ref>。

《[[泰坦尼克号_(1997年电影)|泰坦尼克号]]》赢得了包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]和[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|导演]]在内的11项大奖，是这个夜晚的最大赢家，还追平了奥斯卡金像奖历史上一部电影获奖数量最多的纪录<ref>{{cite news | last = Harden | first = Mark | title = Epic film sails away with Oscar boatload | work = Denver Post | publisher = MediaNews Group | page = A-01 | date = 1998-03-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Weinraub | first = Bernard | title = 'Titanic' Ties Record With 11 Oscars, Including Best Picture | archivedate = 2014-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304171931/http://www.nytimes.com/1998/03/24/movies/titanic-ties-record-with-11-oscars-including-best-picture.html | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1998/03/24/movies/titanic-ties-record-with-11-oscars-including-best-picture.html | accessdate = 2014-03-29 | work = The New York Times | publisher = The New York Times Company | date = 1998-03-24}}</ref>。其它获奖电影包括获奖两项的《[[尽善尽美|尽善尽美]]》、《[[心灵捕手|心灵捕手]]》和《[[洛城机密|洛城机密]]》，获奖一项的《[[黑衣人_(电影)|黑衣人]]》、《[[光豬六壯士|光豬六壯士]]》、《[[棋逢敌手|棋逢敌手]]》、《[[外交官的抉择|外交官的抉择]]》（{{lang|en|''Visas and Virtue''}}）、《[[角色_(电影)|角色]]》（{{lang|nl|''Karakter''}}）、《遥遥归乡路》（{{lang|en|''The Long Way Home''}}）以及《复原的故事》（{{lang|en|''A Story of Healing''}}）。晚会的电视直播平均吸引了超过5700万美国观众收看，创下了历史上的新纪录<ref>{{cite news|last=Scanton |first=Julian |title=Could Avatar Boost Oscar Ratings to Record Heights? |archivedate=2014-03-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312224910/http://www.vanityfair.com/online/oscars/2010/01/could-avatar-boost-oscar-ratings-to-record-heights |url=http://www.vanityfair.com/online/oscars/2010/01/could-avatar-boost-oscar-ratings-to-record-heights |accessdate=2014-03-29 |work=Vanity Fair |publisher=Condé Nast |date=2010-01-27 }}</ref>。

== 获奖和提名 ==
第70届奥斯卡金像奖提名名单于1998年1月27日由学院主席罗伯特·莱姆（{{lang|en|Robert Rehme}}）和女演员[[吉娜·戴维斯|吉娜·戴维斯]]一起在[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的[[塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院|塞缪尔·戈尔德温剧院]]公布<ref>{{cite news | title = 'Titanic' cruises into Oscars lead | url = http://edition.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/9802/10/oscar.nominations/ | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = CNN | publisher = TimeWarner | date = 1998-02-10 | archivedate = 2013-11-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131103083024/http://www.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/9802/10/oscar.nominations/}}</ref>。《泰坦尼克号》以多达14项提名领跑，还追平了《[[彗星美人|彗星美人]]》创下的提名纪录（再次出現入圍14項的影片為[[第89屆奧斯卡金像獎|第89屆奧斯卡金像獎]]的《[[樂來越愛你|樂來越愛你]]》），《心灵捕手》和《洛城机密》均以9项提名排在第二位<ref>{{cite news | last = Ebert | first = Roger | title = Oscar hopefuls"Titanic' ties a record; DiCaprio misses boat | work = Denver Post | publisher = MediaNews Group | page = F-01 | date = 1998-02-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = `Titanic' lands 14 Oscar nominations; ties 1950 record | work = U-T San Diego | publisher = MLIM Holdings | page = A-3 | date = 1998-02-11}}</ref>。

获奖名单在1998年3月23日举行的颁奖典礼上公布<ref>{{cite news|title=Nominees & Winners for the 70th Academy Awards |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/1990-1999/70nominees.html |accessdate=2014-03-30 |work=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |publisher=AMPAS |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102101037/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/1990-1999/70nominees.html |archivedate=2013-11-02 }}</ref>。获奖11项的《泰勒尼克号》追平了《[[宾虚|宾虚]]》所创获奖最多的电影纪录<ref>{{cite news | last = Rickey | first = Carrie | title = `Titanic' Ties Record With 11 Oscars; `Good As It Gets' Takes Acting Honors | url = http://articles.philly.com/1998-03-24/news/25745927_1_host-billy-crystal-oscar-telecast-supporting-actor | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = The Philadelphia Inquirer | publisher = Philadelphia Media Network | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131105035145/http://articles.philly.com/1998-03-24/news/25745927_1_host-billy-crystal-oscar-telecast-supporting-actor | archivedate = 2013-11-05 | deadurl = no | date = 1998-03-24}}</ref>。影片也成为继1965年的《[[音乐之声_(电影)|音乐之声]]》以来首部没有获得[[编剧|编剧]]类奖项提名而拿下最佳影片奖的电影<ref>{{cite news | last = Guthmann | first = Edward| title = 'Titanic' Rides an Oscar Tidal Wave / But Hunt and Nicholson take the top acting awards | archivedate = 2013-11-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131103212932/http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/Titanic-Rides-an-Oscar-Tidal-Wave-But-Hunt-3011161.php | url = http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/Titanic-Rides-an-Oscar-Tidal-Wave-But-Hunt-3011161.php | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = San Francisco Chronicle | publisher = Hearst Corporation |date= 1998-03-24}}</ref>。[[奥斯卡最佳女主角奖|女主角奖]]得主[[海伦·亨特|海伦·亨特]]成为第一位获奥斯卡奖同时还在主演[[电视节目|电视节目]]的演员<ref>{{cite news | last = Dirks | first = Tim | title = 1997 Academy Awards Winners and History | url = http://www.filmsite.org/aa97.html | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = Filmsite | publisher = AMC Networks | archivedate = 2013-11-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131102180641/http://www.filmsite.org/aa97.html}}</ref>，[[杰克·尼科尔森|杰克·尼科尔森]]成为第四位获得三项表演类奖项的演员<ref>{{cite news | last = Glaister | first = Dan | title = Titanic sinks British Oscar hopes | work = The Guardian |date= 1998-03-25 | publisher = Guardian Media Group | page = 5}}</ref>，两人都是因《尽善尽美》获奖，该片也成为历史上第七部斩获影帝影后两项桂冠的电影<ref>{{cite book | last = Symons | first = Mitchell | title = That Book ...of Perfectly Useless Information | year = 2004 | isbn = 978-0-06-073254-7 | location = New York, United States | edition = | OCLC =  | publisher = HarperCollins | page = 138}}</ref>。[[凯特·温丝莱特|凯特·温丝莱特]]和[[格劳瑞亚·斯图尔特|格劳瑞亚·斯图尔特]]因在《泰坦尼克号》中分别扮演年轻和年老时的罗斯·德威特·布卡特（{{lang|en|Rose DeWitt Bukater}}）而分获女主角奖及[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|女配角奖]]提名，这也是电影史上首次有两位女演员在同一部电影中饰演同一角色并双双获表演奖提名<ref>{{cite news|last=Germain |first=David |title=Gloria Stuart, 'Titanic' co-star, dies at 100 |archivedate=2013-11-05 |url=http://seattletimes.com/html/entertainment/2013009486_apusobitgloriastuart.html |accessdate=2014-03-30 |work=The Seattle Times |publisher=The Seattle Times Company |date=2010-09-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105035104/http://seattletimes.com/html/entertainment/2013009486_apusobitgloriastuart.html }}</ref>。同时斯图尔特获提名时已是87岁高龄，创下提名人数年龄的最高纪录<ref>{{cite news | last = Scott | first = Andrew | title = Gloria Stuart, Star of 'Titanic,' Dead at 100 | url = http://news.moviefone.com/2010/09/27/gloria-stuart-dead/ | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = Moviefone | publisher = AOL | date = 2010-09-27 | archivedate = 2013-11-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131104005804/http://news.moviefone.com/2010/09/27/gloria-stuart-dead/ | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

