== 典礼资讯 ==
[[File:Billy_Crystal_VF_2012_Shankbone.JPG|thumb]]担任第70届奥斯卡颁奖典礼主持人。]]
1997年12月，[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]聘请了资深奥斯卡电视转播[[制作人|制作人]]吉尔·凯茨担任1998年颁奖典礼的制片人<ref name="Cates">{{cite news | last = Hindes | first = Andrew | title = And Cates makes eight | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140307193437/http://variety.com/1997/film/news/and-cates-makes-eight-1116680279/ | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/1997/film/news/and-cates-makes-eight-1116680279/ | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 1997-12-11 | archivedate = 2014-03-07}}</ref>。对此学院主席罗伯特·莱姆在新闻发布会上称：“吉尔已经成为完美的奥斯卡节目制作人，他一直都能够为电视转播赢得最高的收视率。他的节目中充满了机智、魅力和惊喜。”<ref name="Cates" />几天后，凯茨选择了喜剧演员比利·克里斯托担任晚会的主持人，他表示：“比利在去年的表现可谓无与伦比，没有（别的）任何人能够做得像他这样（出色）”<ref>{{cite news | title = News Lite Veteran DJ Will End Storied Career | accessdate = 2014-01-26 | work = Los Angeles Daily News | publisher = MediaNews Group | date = 1997-12-20 | page = N2}}</ref>。根据《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》上发表的一篇文章，克里斯托曾在[[第69届奥斯卡金像奖|去年颁奖典礼]]五个月后向凯茨和学院表示，自己希望暂时休息一阵，不做主持人了。然而，来自学院、凯茨和多位家人、朋友的压力还是让他重新考虑了自己的决定<ref name="Bona" />{{rp|156}}。这第六次主持也让他主持的奥斯卡颁奖典礼次数仅次于[[鲍勃·霍普|鲍勃·霍普]]<ref name="Bona" />{{rp|157}}。

为了纪念奥斯卡金像奖七十周年，晚会中的一个称为奥斯卡大家庭相册的环节中将有70位曾获过奖的演员一起出现在舞台上<ref name="Pond">{{cite book | last = Pond | first = Steve | title = The Big Show: High Times and Dirty Dealings Backstage at the Academy Awards | url = https://archive.org/details/bigshowhightimes00pond | year = 2005 | isbn = 0-571-21193-3 | location = New York, United States | edition = | OCLC =  | publisher = Faber and Faber}}</ref>{{rp|185}}，报幕员诺曼·罗斯（{{lang|en|Norman Rose}}）将会报出各位演员及其获奖的电影片名。到片段末尾时，本届晚会上的获奖演员金·贝辛格、海伦·亨特和罗宾·威廉斯都将加入他们的行列。这也成为继1978年举行的[[第50届奥斯卡金像奖|第50届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]以来聚集过去获奖者最多的一次<ref name="Bona" />{{rp|177}}。

另外还有多人参与了颁奖典礼的制作。[[比尔·康堤|比尔·康堤]]（{{lang|en|Bill Conti}}）担任晚会的音乐总监<ref>{{cite news | title = Conti named musical director of 70th Academy Awards | url = http://variety.com/1998/more/news/jan-14-1998-1117436386/ | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 1998-01-13 | archivedate = 2014-02-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140226134308/http://variety.com/1998/more/news/jan-14-1998-1117436386/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。舞蹈家丹尼尔·艾兹拉洛（{{lang|en|Daniel Ezralow}}）编排了音乐剧和喜剧类原创配乐奖提名作品的现场歌舞<ref name="Pond" />{{rp|170}}。[[巴特熊|巴特熊]]还意外出现在晚会现场，与男演员[[麦克·迈尔斯|麦克·迈尔斯]]一起颁发了音效奖<ref name="Pond" />{{rp|168}}。

=== 提名电影票房表现 ===
截止2月10日提名名单公布时，五部获最佳影片提名电影在[[美国电影|美国]]的总计[[票房|票房]]收入为5亿7881万4463美元，平均每部1亿1576万2893美元<ref name="BoxOfficeOscars">{{cite news | title = 1997 Academy Award Nominations and Winner for Best Picture | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=1997&p=.htm | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | publisher = Amazon.com | archivedate = 2014-03-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140329025412/http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=1997&p=.htm}}</ref>。其中《泰坦尼克号》以3亿3871万零764[[美元|美元]]位居榜首<ref name="BoxOfficeOscars" />，之后分别是收入9263万7620美元的《尽善尽美》，进账6886万5287美元的《心灵捕手》，收入3973万8569美元的《洛城机密》和进账3886万2223美元的《光豬六壯士》<ref name="BoxOfficeOscars" />。

在1997年美国电影票房50强中，有15部电影获得了共计40项提名。只有《泰坦尼克号》（[[冠军|冠军]]）、《尽善尽美》（第16位）、《心灵捕手》（第20位》和《新郎向后跑》（第24位）四部获得了最佳影片、导演，或表演、编剧类奖项提名<ref name="boxofficemojooscars">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-11-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131103210153/http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=1998-02-10&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=1997&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?asof=1998-02-10&view=releasedate&view2=domestic&yr=1997&sort=gross&order=DESC&p=.htm | title = 1997 Domestic Grosses | publisher = Amazon.com | work = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2014-03-30}}</ref>。另外11部获提名的分别是《黑衣人》（[[亚军|亚军]]）、《侏罗纪公园：失落的世界》（[[季军|季军]]）、《空军一号》（第5位）、《我最好朋友的婚礼》（第7位）、《变脸》（第9位）、《空中监狱》（第12位）、《超时空接触》（第13位）、《大力士》（第14位）、《第五元素》（第25位）、《安娜斯塔西娅》（第30位）和《星河战队》（第34位）<ref name="boxofficemojooscars" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
本场晚会获得了大部分媒体的正面评价。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》电视评论员霍华德·罗森伯格（{{lang|en|Howard Rosenberg}}）称赞主持人克里斯托把[[音乐剧|音乐剧]]和[[喜剧|喜剧]]当成笑料的巧妙做法值得最高的评价<ref>{{cite news | last = Rosenberg | first = Howard | title = Crystal Persuasion | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1998/mar/24/entertainment/ca-32299 | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 1998-03-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140221173400/http://articles.latimes.com/1998/mar/24/entertainment/ca-32299 | archivedate = 2014-02-21}}</ref>。《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》专栏作家约翰·卡门（{{lang|en|John Carman}}）对节目赞不绝口：“这是20年来最优秀的奥斯卡颁奖典礼。”他对主持人予以高度评价，称克里斯托在这个夜晚的表现非常犀利<ref>{{cite news | last = Carman | first = John | title = Oscar Polishes Up His Image / Crystal clearly a winner for best show in decades | url = http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Oscar-Polishes-Up-His-Image-Crystal-clearly-a-3011121.php | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = San Francisco Chronicle | publisher = Hearst Corporation | date = 1998-03-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140202225702/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Oscar-Polishes-Up-His-Image-Crystal-clearly-a-3011121.php | archivedate = 2014-02-02}}</ref>。《[[西雅图时报|西雅图时报]]》电视栏目主编凯·麦克法登（{{lang|en|Kay McFadden}}）也称赞了克里斯托的表现，称他对时机的把握和判断能力上都近乎无懈可击。此外，她还认为晚会时长虽然一拖再拖，但这仍然是自己印象中近来电视上最具智慧的现场晚会直播节目<ref>{{cite news | last = McFadden | first = Kay | title = Ceremony Shapes Up As A Night To Remember | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201200513/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=19980324&slug=2741394 | url = http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=19980324&slug=2741394 | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = The Seattle Times | publisher = The Seattle Times Company | date = 1998-03-24}}</ref>。

不过也有部分媒体对节目的表现予以负面评价。《[[综艺|综艺]]》的雷·里奇蒙（{{lang|en|Ray Richmond}}）抱怨节目让人晕晕欲睡，还批评克里斯托只会说一些俏皮话，让节目沉沦得“比那艘巨轮还要快”<ref>{{cite news | last = Richmond | first = Ray | title = Review: ‘The 70th Annual Academy Awards’| archivedate = 2014-02-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140225005701/http://variety.com/1998/tv/reviews/the-70th-annual-academy-awards-1200453061/ | url = http://variety.com/1998/tv/reviews/the-70th-annual-academy-awards-1200453061/ | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = Variety | publisher = PMC | date = 1998-03-23}}</ref>。《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》（{{lang|en|''Boston Globe''}}）电视评论员马修·吉尔伯特（{{lang|en|Matthew Gilbert}}）哀叹道：“昨晚的奥斯卡晚会几乎没有一个自由发挥的瞬间”<ref>{{cite news | last = Gilbert | first = Matthew | title = Telecast Sinks Under TIred Bits, Little Spark | accessdate = 2014-01-23 | newspaper = Boston Globe | date = 1998-03-24 | page = D1}}</ref>。《[[费城问询报|费城问询报]]》影评人卡丽·瑞基（{{lang|en|Carrie Rickey}}）感叹，《泰坦尼克号》不可避免地横扫了这个满载过往奥斯卡亮点片段而沉没的夜晚<ref>{{cite news | last = Rickey | first = Carey | title = `Titanic' Ties Record With 11 Oscars; `Good As It Gets' Takes Acting Honors | url = http://articles.philly.com/1998-03-24/news/25745927_1_host-billy-crystal-oscar-telecast-supporting-actor | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = The Philadelphia Inquirer | publisher = Philadelphia Media Network | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131105035145/http://articles.philly.com/1998-03-24/news/25745927_1_host-billy-crystal-oscar-telecast-supporting-actor | archivedate = 2013-11-05 | deadurl = no | date = 1998-03-24}}</ref>。

=== 收视率和奖项 ===
本届颁奖典礼通过美国广播公司在美国直播，其播出时段里平均有5725万观众收看，与[[第69届奥斯卡金像奖|去年]]相比提高了29%<ref>{{cite news | last = Crupi | first = Anthony | title = ABC Strikes Gold With the Oscars | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131103090449/http://www.adweek.com/news/television/abc-strikes-gold-oscars-147081 | url = http://www.adweek.com/news/television/abc-strikes-gold-oscars-147081 | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = Adweek | publisher = Prometheus Global Media | date = 2013-02-06 | archivedate = 2013-11-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，而所有曾观看部分播出时段节目的观众总数则估计有8750万<ref name="Pond" />{{rp|187}}。从尼尔森收视率调查的数量看，节目的表现也好过之前，吸引了34.9%的[[家庭|家庭]]观看<ref name="TVB Oscars">{{cite news|title=Academy Awards ratings |work=''Television Bureau of Advertising'' |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |archivedate=2013-09-27 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.tvb.org/media/file/Academy_Awards.pdf |accessdate=2014-02-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927155318/http://www.tvb.org/media/file/Academy_Awards.pdf }}</ref>，在18至49岁年龄段观众群的收视率为24.2%<ref name="TVB Oscars" />。这也是继1974年[[第46届奥斯卡金像奖|第46届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]开始汇编收视率数字以来的最高收视纪录<ref>{{cite web | first = Bill | last = Gorman | title = Academy Awards Averages 41.3 Million Viewers; Most Since 2005 | archivedate = 2013-11-01 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131101231748/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/03/08/academy-awards-averages-41-3-million-viewers-most-since-2005/44217/ | work = TV by the Numbers | date = 2010-03-08 | publisher = Tribune Company | url = http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/03/08/academy-awards-averages-41-3-million-viewers-most-since-2005/44217/ | accessdate = 2014-03-30 }}</ref>。

1998年7月，颁奖典礼获得了第50届[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]的8项提名<ref>{{cite news | title = Primetime Emmy Award database | url = http://www.emmys.com/shows/70th-annual-academy-awards | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = Academy of Television Arts and Sciences | publisher = ATAS | archivedate = 2012-10-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121001085632/http://www.emmys.com/shows/70th-annual-academy-awards}}</ref>，并在两个月后赢得了五项大奖，分别是综艺或音乐节目类杰出个人表现奖（比利·克里斯托），综艺或音乐节目类杰出导演奖（路易斯·{{lang|en|J}}·霍维茨），剧情、综艺、迷你剧或电影类杰出照明指导奖，杰出音乐总监（比尔·康堤）以及综艺或特别节目类杰出音效奖<ref>{{cite news | title = The Emmy Winners Announced on Saturday | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1998/aug/31/entertainment/ca-18105 | accessdate = 2014-03-30 | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Tribune Company | date = 1998-08-31 | archive-date = 2013-11-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131106080823/http://articles.latimes.com/1998/aug/31/entertainment/ca-18105 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = 1998 Emmy Winners | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131114083821/http://www.nytimes.com/1998/09/15/arts/the-1998-emmy-winners.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1998/09/15/arts/the-1998-emmy-winners.html | accessdate = 2014-03-30 |work=The New York Times | publisher = The New York Times Company | date = 1998-09-15 | archivedate = 2013-11-14}}</ref>。

